name: Swift Impact
description:
The goal is simple. Don't let the enemies touch you for as long as you can. Easier said than done.

With a barrage of non stop enemies charging at you it provides hours of entertainment and replay-ability.
It's a fast paced game that will keep you on edge. It's easy to play, but hard to master.

This game is my first app I have ever published and I thank you for your support and hope you will enjoy future games I create.
